<p>Cuba has told international airlines it is running low on jet fuel and will pause refuelling for about a month—a move that could disrupt flights and further squeeze tourism, one of the island’s main sources of hard currency. The pause comes as authorities roll out fuel-rationing measures to keep essential services running during a wider energy crunch that has already hit transport, public services, and other parts of the economy.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/wuv3iml_os0yOus_y5xMf_jmNB7ptZhm7GbPkC-AjU1_3GbXcLdgHfs8FL4xFZRnSbbNUicmbxFrqoplpWs38JbT54kl-gm7Z3yKQu7KrCLBSDm2nXeIeGx43KU9Q-QKoERDHQKTl91U8AMUPnVD-63IaaWqP3S9y6nUu1iQ5NEQeUoNVbhIxwbw62SN3aYKRv66vHpUsjG7kwI-hpSI_ytccB7A9bojE7PRJot2YkYNNv5NoTlf-9YZ7zjArSsTZV7B7F4jMRrJDODI5Q' alt='People wait for transportation as Cubans brace for fuel scarcity measures in Havana, Feb. 6, 2026.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Economic curbs: Semafor said authorities have had to shut down parts of the economy as fuel supplies tighten.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Kremlin (Russia): The Kremlin called Cuba’s fuel situation “critical” and accused the United States of trying to “suffocate” the island’s economy. (<a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-fuel-situation-in-cuba-is-critical-accuses-us-of-suffocating-the-island'>The Straits Times</a>)</li><li>Cuban authorities: Cuba rolled out fuel-rationing steps aimed at protecting essential services as shortages deepen. (<a href='https://www.theglobeandmail.com/world/article-cuba-fuel-crisis-russia-us/'>The Globe and Mail</a>)</li><li>Cuban government: Havana told airlines it cannot refuel planes traveling to the country because the island is running out of fuel. (<a href='https://www.semafor.com/article/02/09/2026/cuba-unable-to-refuel-planes-as-oil-crisis-deepens'>Semafor</a>)</li><li>Semafor/reporting: Semafor described Washington as seeking Cuba’s regime change, which Havana has vowed to resist. (<a href='https://www.semafor.com/article/02/09/2026/cuba-unable-to-refuel-planes-as-oil-crisis-deepens'>Semafor</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-fuel-situation-in-cuba-is-critical-accuses-us-of-suffocating-the-island'>Kremlin says fuel situation in Cuba is critical, accuses US of &#x27;suffocating&#x27; the island</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/world/cuba-suspends-airline-refuelling-as-us-punishment-triggers-energy-crisis-13977602.html'>Cuba suspends airline refuelling as US punishment triggers energy crisis</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theglobeandmail.com/world/article-cuba-fuel-crisis-russia-us/'>Russia accuses U.S. of ‘suffocating’ Cuba as fuel crisis deepens</a> - theglobeandmail.com</li><li><a href='https://www.semafor.com/article/02/09/2026/cuba-unable-to-refuel-planes-as-oil-crisis-deepens'>Cuba unable to refuel planes as oil crisis deepens</a> - semafor.com</li><li><a href='https://en.mercopress.com/2026/02/09/cuba-tells-airlines-it-will-run-out-of-jet-fuel-as-of-monday-deepening-energy-crisis'>Cuba tells airlines it will run out of jet fuel as of Monday, deepening energy crisis</a> - mercopress.com</li></ul>